    <h2 class="my-0">Comment Indent</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="col-auto">
    <code>commentIndent</code>
  </div>
</div>
Applies single indentation to containing content of Liquid comments. Liquid line type comments are currently not supported by this rule. Only block type Liquid tokens will be handled. Liquid line type comments are currently not supported by this rule. Only block type Liquid tokens will be handled.

<div class="row py-4">
  <div class="col-2">
